                <note rend="inline" type="source">863.00/883: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Austria</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Earle</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Vienna</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-02-28T14:00:00+01:00"
                            >February 28, 1934—2 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 28—9:25 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>38. My telegram No. 37 of today. Proposed statement has full approval Austrian
                    Foreign Office.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Earle</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
